---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Squatch Marketing is a full-service marketing agency in Salt Lake City, Utah. We help businesses grow with digital marketing, content design, web development, and email campaigns. Meet the team behind the results."
>

  <!-- ========== HERO ========== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center gradient-mesh noise overflow-hidden" aria-label="About Hero">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute top-[5%] right-[10%] w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-blue/[0.08] blur-[160px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="orb-drift-reverse absolute bottom-[10%] left-[-5%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-teal/[0.06] blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pt-36 lg:pt-44 pb-20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-teal/[0.08] border border-teal/[0.12]">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal animate-pulse"></div>
              <span class="text-teal text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Salt Lake City</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-display font-800 text-[clamp(2.5rem,5.5vw,4.5rem)] text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.03em] mb-7">
          Built different.<br />
          <span class="text-gradient">On purpose.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-lg lg:text-xl text-white/35 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          We started Squatch because too many agencies treat clients like line items. We thought the industry needed a team that actually gives a damn.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-40 bg-gradient-to-t from-void to-transparent pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== WHY WE STARTED ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-28 bg-void overflow-hidden" aria-label="Our Story">
    <div class="orb-drift-reverse absolute top-[20%] right-[5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-blue/[0.04] blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Story -->
        <div>
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-blue/[0.08] border border-blue/[0.12]">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue animate-pulse"></div>
              <span class="text-blue text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Our Story</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-display font-800 text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem)] text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] mb-8">
            Why we <span class="text-gradient">started Squatch</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 space-y-5 text-white/35 text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              We watched businesses get locked into bloated contracts with agencies that barely knew their name. Monthly reports full of vanity metrics. Cookie-cutter strategies. Zero accountability.
            </p>
            <p>
              That didn't sit right with us. So we built something different. A small, focused team that treats every client like our only client. We learn your business. We learn your customers. Then we build marketing that actually works.
            </p>
            <p>
              No fluff. No filler. Just people who care about your growth as much as you do.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Visual -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="glass-strong rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10 relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue/[0.03] via-transparent to-teal/[0.03] rounded-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 space-y-8">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-1">Full-service, zero excuses</h3>
                  <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">Strategy, design, development, campaigns. One team handles it all so nothing falls through the cracks.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-1">Small team, big commitment</h3>
                  <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">We keep our client roster intentionally tight. That means you get real attention, not an intern and a template.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-1">Results you can measure</h3>
                  <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">We track what matters. Revenue, leads, growth. Not impressions and likes that don't pay the bills.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- ========== VALUES ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-28 section-mesh overflow-hidden" aria-label="Our Values">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute bottom-[10%] left-[30%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-teal/[0.04] blur-[140px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="noise absolute inset-0"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <div class="reveal">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-teal/[0.08] border border-teal/[0.12]">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal animate-pulse"></div>
              <span class="text-teal text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Our Values</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-display font-800 text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem)] text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em]">
          Values that aren't just <span class="text-gradient">wall art</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Value 1 -->
        <div class="reveal glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-3">Partners, not vendors</h3>
          <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">You're not a revenue source to us. You're a partner. Your wins are our wins. Your problems keep us up at night too.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 2 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-3">All in, every time</h3>
          <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">Half-effort isn't in our vocabulary. When we take on a project, we commit fully. Your success is the only acceptable outcome.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 3 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 010-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.963-7.178z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-3">Radical transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">No smoke and mirrors. You see what we see. Real data, honest assessments, and straight talk about what's working and what's not.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 4 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455 2.456zM16.894 20.567L16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 001.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 001.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423 1.423z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-3">Stay sharp, stay curious</h3>
          <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">Marketing moves fast. We're always testing new tools, learning new platforms, and finding better ways to get you results.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 5 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-4 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 8.511c.884.284 1.5 1.128 1.5 2.097v4.286c0 1.136-.847 2.1-1.98 2.193-.34.027-.68.052-1.02.072v3.091l-3-3c-1.354 0-2.694-.055-4.02-.163a2.115 2.115 0 01-.825-.242m9.345-8.334a2.126 2.126 0 00-.476-.095 48.64 48.64 0 00-8.048 0c-1.131.094-1.976 1.057-1.976 2.192v4.286c0 .837.46 1.58 1.155 1.951m9.345-8.334V6.637c0-1.621-1.152-3.026-2.76-3.235A48.455 48.455 0 0011.25 3c-2.115 0-4.198.137-6.24.402-1.608.209-2.76 1.614-2.76 3.235v6.226c0 1.621 1.152 3.026 2.76 3.235.577.075 1.157.14 1.74.194V21l4.155-4.155" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-3">Communicate like humans</h3>
          <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">No jargon walls. No reports you need a PhD to read. We talk to you like real people because that's what we are.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 6 -->
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-5 glass-interactive rounded-2xl p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17l-5.1-5.1m0 0L11.42 4.97m-5.1 5.1H21M3 3v18" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display font-700 text-white text-lg mb-3">Every business deserves great marketing</h3>
          <p class="text-white/30 text-sm leading-relaxed">Startups, local shops, enterprise companies. Your size doesn't determine the quality of marketing you deserve. We serve all of them.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- ========== UTAH CONNECTION ========== -->
  <section class="relative py-28 bg-void overflow-hidden" aria-label="Utah Roots">
    <div class="orb-drift absolute top-[15%] left-[60%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-blue/[0.05] blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <!-- Left: Visual element -->
        <div class="reveal order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-1.5 glow">
            <div class="bg-abyss/90 rounded-xl overflow-hidden p-8 lg:p-10">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div class="space-y-6">
                  <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/[0.04]">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-white/40 mb-1 font-medium">Based in</div>
                    <div class="text-white font-display font-700 text-sm">West Valley City, UT</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/[0.04]">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-white/40 mb-1 font-medium">Serving</div>
                    <div class="text-white font-display font-700 text-sm">Clients Nationwide</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                  <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/[0.04]">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-white/40 mb-1 font-medium">Team</div>
                    <div class="text-white font-display font-700 text-sm">Small & Focused</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white/[0.03] rounded-xl p-5 border border-white/[0.04]">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-xs text-white/40 mb-1 font-medium">Call us</div>
                    <div class="text-white font-display font-700 text-sm">801-803-2136</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Copy -->
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="reveal">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-blue/[0.08] border border-blue/[0.12]">
              <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue animate-pulse"></div>
              <span class="text-blue text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide">Utah Roots</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-display font-800 text-[clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem)] text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] mb-8">
            Mountains breed <span class="text-gradient">work ethic</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 space-y-5 text-white/35 text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              We're based in West Valley City, just minutes from the Wasatch Range. When we're not building campaigns, you'll find us snowboarding, fly fishing, or camping somewhere with no cell service.
            </p>
            <p>
              Utah taught us something: if you want results, you put in the work. No shortcuts. No summit without the climb. That mindset runs through everything we do for our clients.
            </p>
            <p>
              The Salt Lake City tech scene is booming, and we're proud to be part of it. But we work with businesses everywhere. Local coffee shop or national brand, the approach is the same: understand your business, build the right strategy, execute relentlessly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
